subject: Basketball
lead_paragraph: Tyler Hansbrough had 22 points and a career-high 21 rebounds and No. 4 North Carolina beat host Florida State, 84-73, in overtime Sunday. The Tar Heels lost their starting point guard, Ty Lawson, four minutes into the game when he sprained his left ankle.
